    <h1 class="heading1">Cosmetic Surgery Department at Aatura Hospital</h1>
    <h4 class="heading4">At Aatura Hospital, our Cosmetic Surgery Department is dedicated to helping patients achieve their aesthetic goals and enhance their appearance through safe and effective surgical procedures. Led by experienced plastic surgeons and supported by a team of skilled healthcare professionals, we offer a wide range of cosmetic surgical procedures tailored to meet the unique needs and desires of each patient.</h4>

    <div class="content1">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h3>Our Services</h3>
            <h4>Facial Rejuvenation</h4>
            <p>We offer a variety of facial rejuvenation procedures to address signs of aging and improve facial contours. These may include facelifts, brow lifts, eyelid surgery (blepharoplasty), neck lifts, and fat grafting to restore volume and youthful appearance to the face.</p>

            <h4>Rhinoplasty (Nose Surgery)</h4>
            <p>Rhinoplasty is a surgical procedure to reshape the nose and improve its appearance or function. Our plastic surgeons perform rhinoplasty to correct nasal asymmetry, reduce or increase the size of the nose, refine the nasal tip, or address breathing problems.</p>

            <h4>Breast Augmentation, Lift, and Reduction</h4>
            <p>We offer breast enhancement procedures, including breast augmentation with implants, breast lift (mastopexy), and breast reduction surgery. These procedures can improve breast size, shape, symmetry, and overall appearance, enhancing self-confidence and body image.</p>

            <h4>Body Contouring</h4>
            <p>Body contouring procedures are designed to reshape and enhance body contours by removing excess fat, skin, and tissue. Our cosmetic surgeons perform procedures such as liposuction, tummy tuck (abdominoplasty), body lift, thigh lift, and arm lift to achieve a more sculpted and toned appearance.</p>

            <h4>Liposuction</h4>
            <p>Liposuction is a surgical procedure to remove localized fat deposits and improve body contours. Our plastic surgeons utilize advanced liposuction techniques, such as tumescent liposuction, laser-assisted liposuction, and ultrasound-assisted liposuction, to achieve smoother and more natural-looking results.</p>

            <h4>Non-Surgical Cosmetic Treatments</h4>
            <p>In addition to surgical procedures, we offer a variety of non-surgical cosmetic treatments to rejuvenate the skin and enhance facial features. These may include injectable treatments such as Botox, dermal fillers, and chemical peels to reduce wrinkles, restore volume, and improve skin texture and tone.</p>
        </div>
